         MACRO
&NAME    AUTH  &P
         AIF   ('&NAME' EQ '').START
&NAME    DS    0H
.START   AIF   ('&P' EQ '' OR '&P' NE 'ON').OFF
         SR    1,1 .               LOAD AUTHORIZATION ON CODE
         SVC   233 .               TURN AUTHORIZATION ON
         MEXIT
.OFF     LA    1,4 .               LOAD AUTHORIZATION OFF CODE
         SVC   233 .               TURN AUTHORIZATION OFF
         MEND
